    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "A *jyoti\u2019s feather* is a shimmering red-and-gold feather that seems almost metallic, although it\u2019s delicate and flexible to the touch. Though most aren\u2019t made from true jyoti feathers, as the reclusive outsiders avoid visitors from the Universe, the creatures\u2019 connection to life energy lent these spellhearts their name. \n* **Armor** You gain a +2 item bonus to saving throws against death effects and void effects.\n* **Weapon** The weapon has the *vitalizing* rune while the feather is affixed.",
        "level": 10,
        "traits": [
            {
